---
title: Cal Smart Breaded Chipotle Turkey Scallopini with Enchilada-Spiced Veggie Jumble
description: This dinner is smoky, crunchy and slightly spicy, and is great for a case of the 'blahs'!  Lean turkey and a satisfying veggie jumble meet our signature chipotle sauce and enchilada spices for the weeknight change-up you've been looking for.

